# Local Claude Code config (machine-specific permissions, worktrees, launch cfg).
# Ignore the CONTENTS, not the folder — CLAUDE.md is the project's shared rules
# and must travel with the repo (it mirrors /AGENTS.md; see
# src/lib/project-rules-sync.test.ts). settings.local.json stays local: it holds
# per-machine permission grants.
.claude/*
!.claude/CLAUDE.md

